                            <comment id="15094292" author="alexliu68" created="Tue, 12 Jan 2016 17:01:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It should be OK.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15117889" author="JIRAUSER308715" created="Tue, 26 Jan 2016 20:11:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should upgrade to the GA driver when it comes out. The &quot;beta1&quot; driver included right now is actually a &quot;pre-alpha4&quot; driver, as alpha4 release was originally going to be beta1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15118834" author="snazy" created="Wed, 27 Jan 2016 08:09:35 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;We should upgrade to the GA driver when it comes out. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1 - that&apos;s also necessary for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11064&quot; title=&quot;Failed aggregate creation breaks server permanently&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-11064&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-11064&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;ve got a commit against the latest 3.0.0-SNAPSHOT ready, which includes C* code changes (including the one in this ticket).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15128624" author="snazy" created="Tue, 2 Feb 2016 17:32:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Git branches:&lt;br/&gt;
3.0: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-3.0&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-3.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
3.3: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-3.3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-3.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/snazy/cassandra/tree/11001-java-driver-3.0.0-trunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;utests + dtests look good (except one UFTest in cassci, which has been fixed in the 3.0 branch)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15132541" author="JIRAUSER308715" created="Thu, 4 Feb 2016 16:34:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One fix needed:&lt;br/&gt;
Per the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/datastax/java-driver/tree/3.0/upgrade_guide&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/datastax/java-driver/tree/3.0/upgrade_guide&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;poolingOptions.setMaxSimultaneousRequestsPerConnectionThreshold&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; turned into &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;poolingOptions.setNewConnectionThreshold&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; not &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;poolingOptions.setMaxRequestsPerConnection&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You still have a:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;TODO re-check SSLOptions.DEFAULT_SSL_CIPHER_SUITES&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15132744" author="snazy" created="Thu, 4 Feb 2016 18:37:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;br/&gt;
Committed with the suggested fixes as f34036265ec31b7ffe3a7a43b70be9039d01b544 to 3.0 and merged to trunk (not to 3.3 branch).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
